{"ID":"20260605151617-38fpnzt","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605151617-38fpnzt","title":"2020年新高考Ⅱ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605151634-svbhqsh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-svbhqsh","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠赵伯鱼（节选）"}]},{"ID":"20260605151634-comp1b1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-comp1b1","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"韩  驹"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"①"}]},{"ID":"20260605151634-vha68dj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-vha68dj","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"荆州早识高与黄​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"②"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，诵二子句声琅琅。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151634-h75cpy5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-h75cpy5","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"后生好学果可畏，仆常倦谈殊未详。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151634-q6v5nx5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-q6v5nx5","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学诗当如初学禅，未悟且遍参诸方​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"③"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151634-wpcg1a9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-wpcg1a9","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一朝悟罢正法眼​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"④"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，信手拈出皆成章。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151634-9mly9xr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151634-9mly9xr","updated":"20260605151634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"[注]①韩驹（？～1135），字子苍，两宋之际著名诗人。②高与黄：指前辈诗人高荷与黄庭坚。③参：领悟，琢磨。诸方：各地方，各方面。④正法眼：这里借指事物的诀要或精义。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151617-z1hljpy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151617-z1hljpy","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605151644-r6n0ah3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151644-r6n0ah3","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．下列对这首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605151644-ushq9ej","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151644-ushq9ej","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．从诗的内容可以得知，赵伯鱼是一位勤奋好学、转益多师的诗坛后辈。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151644-8udmo02","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151644-8udmo02","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．诗中使用了古语“后生可畏”，表现出作者对赵伯鱼的嘉许以及劝诫。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151644-fnl5sy5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151644-fnl5sy5","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．面对后辈的请教，作者谦逊地表示，自己所谈不多，也较为简单粗略。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151644-ddbqpud","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151644-ddbqpud","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．诗中以禅理喻诗的内容，既可为赵伯鱼提供指点，也具有普遍的意义。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151644-7fo67lf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151644-7fo67lf","updated":"20260605151644"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．作者主张什么样的学诗途径？请结合诗歌内容简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151617-8mse00z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151617-8mse00z","updated":"20260605151651"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605151617-ul1agsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151617-ul1agsb","updated":"20260605151651"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．B    16．①先要“遍参诸方”，以前人为师，经过长期艰苦的学习；②然后“一朝悟罢”，领悟到诗歌艺术的真旨，就能信手拈出，皆成佳作。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151617-tb941du","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151617-tb941du","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605151702-b8l6d4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151702-b8l6d4t","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查对诗句的理解鉴赏能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151702-qq3mdfq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151702-qq3mdfq","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B项，“劝诫”说法错误，根据诗句“果可畏”可知充满了嘉许、赞赏，并没有劝诫的意思。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151702-sddygfn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151702-sddygfn","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151702-chzib3e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151702-chzib3e","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．本题考查学生理解概括诗句内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151702-soumaxx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151702-soumaxx","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由“学诗当如初学禅，未悟且遍参诸方”，可知作者认为学诗要像初学禅一样，在未开悟的时候，要“遍参诸方”，多琢磨，以诸多前人为师，“遍”、“诸”字强调要下苦功，经过长期艰苦的学习；"}]},{"ID":"20260605151702-hisj0wb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151702-hisj0wb","updated":"20260605151702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由“一朝悟罢正法眼，信手拈出皆成章”可知作者强调“悟”，在学习前人之后要有自己对诗歌艺术真旨的领悟，“一朝悟罢”，一旦领悟到，“信手拈出皆成章”就能信手拈出，皆成佳作。诗也就学成了。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151617-n3bx0sw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151617-n3bx0sw","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}